236
00:09:08,422 --> 00:09:09,010
Probably not.

237
00:09:09,106 --> 00:09:10,797
We'll do something when I get back, okay?

238
00:09:10,897 --> 00:09:12,624
Now why don't you go ahead and drive the staircar home

239
00:09:12,743 --> 00:09:14,299
and Buster and I'll leave from here.

240
00:09:14,412 --> 00:09:15,371
Well, be careful.

241
00:09:15,463 --> 00:09:17,877
Hey. Who's tougher than us?

242
